striessee board relationships background mr scott p scharfman serves as a managing director at mill road capital mr scharfman serves as the chief executive officer and president at mrrc hold co he also serves as an advisor at ihatch ventures llc mr scharfman has over two decades of experience as an investor investment banker and corporate executive prior to joining mill road capital mr scharfman served as the senior manager and managing director of the equity capital markets origination group at  robertson stephens prior to robertson he served as the chief financial officer at mercata inc prior to mercata mr scharfman served as a senior managing director and head of the equity capital markets origination group at bear stearns  co prior to bear stearns he served as a senior manager and vice president at the blackstone group investing blackstones funds in a variety of companies as well as advising clients on merger and acquisition strategy mr scharfman began his career in  with the first boston corporation he was on the team that took first boston private in  he is rchairman of the board of prt growing services ltd and rg barry corporation mr scharfman serves as a member of the board of directors of rubios restaurants inc former chairman and has served on galaxy nutritional foods inc and mrrc hold and multiple boards of both public and private companies he has extensive experience trading equities as well as raising capital in initial public offerings both equity and debt secondaries and convertible offerings for companies in a wide variety of industries mr scharfman holds an ab degree from princeton university where he graduated cum laude and was elected to sigma xi the science honorary societyread full background corporate headquarters  greenwich avenuegreenwich connecticut united statesphone fax  board members memberships directorrubios restaurants incpresident and chief executive officermrrc hold copresentdirectorgalaxy nutritional foods inc education ba princeton